Modifications

The original data was modified by Olav Nyvold

Merging the training and the test sets to create one data set.
Extracting the measurements on the mean and standard deviation for each measurement.
Applying descriptive activity names to name the activities in the data set
Applying descriptive variable names labeling the data set.
Creating a tidy data set with the average of each variable for each activity and each subject.

Descriptions

Identififiers

The first two columns - Subject and Activity - are Identifiers.

Subject: the ID of the Subject
Activity: the Name of the Activity performed by the subject when measurements were taken
Measurements

The variables remaining are the calculatd means and standard deviations of the following sets of data:

